Title: 100 Years of the <em>American Economic Review</em>: The Top 20 Articles 
Abstract:
 This paper presents a list of the top 20 articles published in the
 <em>American Economic Review</em> during its first 100 years.	This list
 was assembled in honor of the <em>AER</em>'s one-hundredth anniversary by
 a group of distinguished economists at the request of <em>AER</em>'s
 editor.  A brief description accompanies the citations of each article.
